These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: plum, onion, strawberry, broccoli, lemon, cabbage, garlic
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, malaysian, argentine, canadian, dutch, polish, egyptian
 1. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is not the polish##6
 3. the thai is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 4. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
 5. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
 6. the thai is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 7. the person eating cabbage is somewhere between the person eating onion and the malaysian##7
 8. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1
 9. the canadian is somewhere between the person eating lemon and the argentine##7
10. the argentine is on the left or right of the thai##3
11. the dutch is on the far left##1
12. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
13. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
14. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
15. the person eating lemon is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | strawberry    | plum    | onion | cabbage | broccoli | lemon    | garlic |
| Nationality   | dutch | thai | argentine  | polish   | canadian    | malaysian | egyptian |

