.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: tomato, cauliflower, lettuce, peas, potato, carrot, kiwi
The people have 7 different hobbies: card-games, board-games, reading, collecting, puzzles, writing, traveling
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the person eating kiwi and the person eating cauliflower##7
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating peas##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 6. the person eating carrot is somewhere between the person eating peas and the person who's hobby is reading##7
 7. the person eating potato is somewhere between the person eating peas and the person eating cauliflower##7
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
10. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
11. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person eating kiwi##6
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person eating peas##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | kiwi  | lettuce | carrot | peas | tomato     | potato | cauliflower  |
| Hobby   | reading | writing | board-games  | traveling  | puzzles | collecting      | card-games |

