 3. the fan of rock is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
 4. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of indie##5
 5. the fan of soul is between the fan of indie and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 6. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of funk##7
10. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
11. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is baking is not the fan of soul##6
13. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is baking##7
14. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
15. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
16. the person who's hobby is baking is not the fan of indie##6
17. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
18. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
19. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
