 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the boat##7
 8. the person who's sport is training is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
10. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is sailing##7
12. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
13. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
14. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
15. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
16. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
