 5. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 6. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
 7. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
 8. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
