 9. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
12. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
13. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person driving the tram##7
14. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the bus##1
15. the person driving the van is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
